text: Masatoshi Takahira (born 26 July 1937) is a Japanese wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman featherweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Japan Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Nagasaki
